Published on Sep 4, 2013

MNsure is the single best, uniquely Minnesotan place to find health insurance. You'll have instant, easy access to coverage options. In addition, we are collaborating with community partners and insurance agents/brokers to create a customer service network that will provide one-to-one assistance.
